name: Car Seat Tent Blanket
description:
Modeled after the very expensive, hard to find "car seat canopy" I present to you the tent!

Made with soft flannel pattern exterior and cuddly "minky" interior the car seat tent blanket is great for solving your blanket worries! This will not blow off your baby carrier even on the windiest of days. Protect your baby from the elements when outside and from curious onlookers when sleeping.

Simply attach the Velcro handles to your car seat, cover the baby up and away you go. 

Custom color requests available. Pictured is the one I made for my family addition coming April 2013. Choose your baby's gender or choose neutral if you don't know yet, and let me know your color/pattern request in your order. Don't know what you want? Tell me your baby room/car seat theme and I'll do the rest!

name: Handmade Chunky Infinity Scarf
description: This seasons hottest "stay warm" item at far below retail price (ie: A&F price $34.00) and the best part, it's handmade in the USA! Only available in 2 colors right now, this chunky infinity scarf will go with all of your cute holiday outfits and your everyday wear! Made with a very soft, 100% acrylic yarn that is machine wash and dry. No itchy feeling around the neck! More colors in the near future. Please email color suggestions to JLynnEqDT@yahoo.com
